title: THE BABIES (us) + JUST FRIENDS AND LOVERS (aut)
description:
The Babies started as a side project led by Cassie Ramone (Vivian Girls) and Kevin Morby (Woods), recording and playing shows in fits and spurts, whenever they all happened to be in town for a week. But in the past two years, the Brooklyn duo has seen the group bloom into another formidable, full-time band and will release a second album "Our House on the Hill" on Nov 13th.
